# Content Repurposing Tests
# Tests for the content repurposing workflow
#
# Prerequisites:
# Set the following environment variable before running the server:
#   OPENAI_API_KEY=<your-openai-api-key>
#
# For posting to social media, each platform needs its own credentials:
#   - LinkedIn: OAuth 2.0 Access Token with w_member_social scope
#   - Twitter: Twitter API v2 Bearer Token
#   - Instagram: Meta Graph API Access Token + Instagram Business Account ID

@baseUrl = http://localhost:13000

### Test repurpose-blog workflow with raw content
# @name repurposeBlogContent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/repurpose-blog
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blogContent": "# The Future of AI in Marketing\n\nArtificial intelligence is revolutionizing how businesses approach marketing. From personalized customer experiences to predictive analytics, AI tools are becoming essential.\n\n## Key Benefits\n\n1. **Personalization at Scale** - AI enables hyper-personalized content for millions of users simultaneously.\n\n2. **Predictive Analytics** - Machine learning models can forecast customer behavior and optimize campaigns.\n\n3. **Automation** - Routine tasks like A/B testing and content scheduling can be fully automated.\n\n## Getting Started\n\nStart small with AI-powered tools like chatbots or email personalization. Measure results and scale what works.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThe future of marketing is intelligent, automated, and deeply personalized. Companies that embrace AI will have a significant competitive advantage.",
  "brand": "TechInsights",
  "tone": "professional"
}

